channel.title: I've installed Moparscape, but it shuts off
channel.description:
Okay, I've installed Moparscape, but whenever I open it up.. it will be at the "Starting Up" on the loading bar, and then it closes the window... help?
Extra Details:
When I had finished installing it, it came up saying that it may not have been installed correctly. So I had the decision to install it again with modifications within my Windows. Then it correctly installed, according to it.
